milestones.description: Mohammad Rafique and Khaled Mashud's 62-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 44 between Khaled Mashud and Hasibul Hossain
This is the lowest match aggregate (289) involving teams West Indies & Bangladesh in ODIs
